<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>纽约时报 &amp;gt; 美国 &amp;gt; 政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/on-politics</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 00:42:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普关于美国财政和伊朗战争的言论指向共和党中期挑战</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/13/us/politics/trump-iran-war-american-finances-republicans-midterms.html</link><description>当被问及是否是出于美国经济困境而达成协议以结束与伊朗的战争时，他回答说：“一点也没有。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 00:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/13/us/politics/trump-iran-war-american-finances-republicans-midterms.html</guid></item><item><title>民主党在纽约初选中的表现如何</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/nyc-midterms-elections-democrats.html</link><description>建制派和左翼领导人正在为分散在城市各处的众议院席位发生冲突。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 21:17:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/nyc-midterms-elections-democrats.html</guid></item><item><title>我们的记者在万斯 2028 年编码之旅期间在爱荷华州看到了什么</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/08/us/politics/jd-vance-iowa-2028.html</link><description>副总统来到该州为弱势的众议院共和党人做竞选演讲，也许还为潜在的总统竞选奠定了一些基础。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 21:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/08/us/politics/jd-vance-iowa-2028.html</guid></item><item><title>密歇根州好斗的民主党参议院初选升温</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/06/us/politics/michigan-senate-primary-democrats.html</link><description>攻击四起，著名的民主党人正在选边站队，战斗才刚刚开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 22:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/06/us/politics/michigan-senate-primary-democrats.html</guid></item><item><title>五月的初选将考验特朗普对共和党的影响力</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/04/us/politics/may-primary-elections-trump-republicans.html</link><description>一系列共和党竞选将考验他对党的控制力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/04/us/politics/may-primary-elections-trump-republicans.html</guid></item><item><title>缅因州参议院竞选的实际情况如何</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/01/us/politics/maine-senate-primary-election.html</link><description>该州是美国参议院最高竞选之一，反建制情绪十分明显。但参议员苏珊·柯林斯也有一些优势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 21:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/01/us/politics/maine-senate-primary-election.html</guid></item><item><title>最高法院通过投票权法案的裁决改变了美国的政治版图</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/29/us/politics/redistricting-maps-supreme-court-voting.html</link><description>双方现在都在争先恐后地适应新的投票权格局。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 21:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/29/us/politics/redistricting-maps-supreme-court-voting.html</guid></item><item><title>从州长竞选到财富税提案，亿万富翁正在主导加州政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/27/us/politics/california-billionaires-tax-governor.html</link><description>在谢尔盖·布林（Sergey Brin）和汤姆·斯泰尔（Tom Steyer）之间，超级富豪正在努力引导国家的方向。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 21:49:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/27/us/politics/california-billionaires-tax-governor.html</guid></item><item><title>中期选举临近时共和党可能采取的策略：负面竞选</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/24/us/politics/republicans-midterms-campaign.html</link><description>共和党人可能会在中期选举中采取久经考验的策略：采取消极态度。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 21:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/24/us/politics/republicans-midterms-campaign.html</guid></item><item><title>为什么弗吉尼亚州的新地图对民主党中期选举很重要，以及下一步是什么</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/22/us/politics/virginia-redistricting-map-democrats-midterms.html</link><description>现在注意力转向佛罗里达州和最高法院。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 21:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/22/us/politics/virginia-redistricting-map-democrats-midterms.html</guid></item></channel></rss>